title: The Snubs and Surprises of the Academy Award Nominations
description:
It appears we have a historic and … good (???) set of nominees for the 93rd Academy Awards. Sean and Amanda dive into all the narratives, break down who missed out and why, and look at which film is likely to take home the big prize on April 25. 

Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins
